#

Fresh Garden Salad with Grilled Chicken

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

high-proteingluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

saladhealthygrilled chicken

Description

A vibrant, refreshing salad topped with juicy grilled chicken, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • mixed greens: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • bell pepper: 1
  • avocado: 1
  • grilled chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
